translation: Make your way toward the Shrine of Seas.{#Name="説明文"}
source: Make your way toward the Shrine of Seas.{#Name="説明文"}

translation: Ah! Aaaah! She's gonna get me!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Ah! Aaaah! She's gonna get me!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: We won't let her lay a finger on Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: We won't let her lay a finger on Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: I'd like to lay somethin' on Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: I'd like to lay somethin' on Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: What the hell? An eye socket is no place to be growin' a flower!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: What the hell? An eye socket is no place to be growin' a flower!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: She gets points for originality...{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: She gets points for originality...{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: So war has come to the Land of Seas...{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: So war has come to the Land of Seas...{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Try not to piss yourself, kid!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Try not to piss yourself, kid!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: If we fight bravely, we might get an audience with Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: If we fight bravely, we might get an audience with Lady Five!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Ooh! And then we'll get to see them beautiful gams!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: Ooh! And then we'll get to see them beautiful gams!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: She's after our Intoner! Stop her, no matter what!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: She's after our Intoner! Stop her, no matter what!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Where are the damn reinforcements!?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Where are the damn reinforcements!?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: The d-dragon... The dragon is...{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: The d-dragon... The dragon is...{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: I thought dragons didn't care about people! What's going on!?{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: I thought dragons didn't care about people! What's going on!?{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: She's somehow able to control that dragon...{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: She's somehow able to control that dragon...{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Keep your sword up, fool! You want to die?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Keep your sword up, fool! You want to die?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: You think the rest of us are ENJOYING this!?{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: You think the rest of us are ENJOYING this!?{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: She's with Dito! She's safe!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: She's with Dito! She's safe!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Bah! Why does she waste time with that pathetic kid?{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Bah! Why does she waste time with that pathetic kid?{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Our lives are sacrifice to our mighty Intoner!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Our lives are sacrifice to our mighty Intoner!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Just once...before I died...I wanted to be with Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Just once...before I died...I wanted to be with Lady Five...{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: We can't hold her! We need support!{#Name="Soldier D"}
source: We can't hold her! We need support!{#Name="Soldier D"}

translation: Her blade is so fast...{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Her blade is so fast...{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: Is it skill? Or something else?{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: Is it skill? Or something else?{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: Get away! Get away from me!{#Name="Soldier G"}
source: Get away! Get away from me!{#Name="Soldier G"}

translation: We can't make contact with any of our allies...{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: We can't make contact with any of our allies...{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: If this keeps up, we're all gonna be worm food!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: If this keeps up, we're all gonna be worm food!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Wow, look at all of them! They're everywhere!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Wow, look at all of them! They're everywhere!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: They're like ants to you. Just crush 'em.{#Name="Zero"}
source: They're like ants to you. Just crush 'em.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Wow, look at the water here! It's so pretty!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Wow, look at the water here! It's so pretty!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Just sink the goddamn battleship, will you?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Just sink the goddamn battleship, will you?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I don't think I can break this barricade.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I don't think I can break this barricade.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Guess I'll just have to climb up and go{LF}around somehow.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Guess I'll just have to climb up and go{LF}around somehow.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Heh. That's a pretty half-assed way to{LF}try and slow me down...{#Name="Zero"}
source: Heh. That's a pretty half-assed way to{LF}try and slow me down...{#Name="Zero"}

translation: So...what kind of sister is Five?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: So...what kind of sister is Five?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It means all she thinks about is dirty stuff.{#Name="Zero"}
source: It means all she thinks about is dirty stuff.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh. So she's just like you!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh. So she's just like you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Looks like people used to live here at some point.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Looks like people used to live here at some point.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Must be nice living near the sea.{LF}Think of all the yummy fish!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Must be nice living near the sea.{LF}Think of all the yummy fish!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: What the hell? Where's the shrine?{#Name="Zero"}
source: What the hell? Where's the shrine?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Dammit. I think we've been had.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Dammit. I think we've been had.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: だって、戦わなくてもよくなったもん{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: だって、戦わなくてもよくなったもん{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: Heh. What are you looking at, shithead?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Heh. What are you looking at, shithead?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Heh. Look at this. Why are big guys{LF}so slow and stupid?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Heh. Look at this. Why are big guys{LF}so slow and stupid?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You don't have to say it twice!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: You don't have to say it twice!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Whatever it is, if it gets in my way,{LF}it's going down.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Whatever it is, if it gets in my way,{LF}it's going down.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Just be careful, Zero! This guy's strong!{LF}Super strong!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Just be careful, Zero! This guy's strong!{LF}Super strong!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Pfft. She thinks that'll be enough to stop me?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Pfft. She thinks that'll be enough to stop me?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Heh. They're really rolling out the red carpet.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Heh. They're really rolling out the red carpet.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: All right, Five. Let's see what you've got.{#Name="Zero"}
source: All right, Five. Let's see what you've got.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: So...what happens once you kill all your sisters?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: So...what happens once you kill all your sisters?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Oh...uh... Ha ha! I totally believed you!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Oh...uh... Ha ha! I totally believed you!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Once I kill them, I can exploit their powers.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Once I kill them, I can exploit their powers.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: So you're going steal their Intoner magic{LF}and stuff?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: So you're going steal their Intoner magic{LF}and stuff?{#Name="Mikhail"}
